00:42:53,620 --> 00:42:54,620
Secretary General Ding, you're coming.

851
00:42:54,620 --> 00:42:55,770
Come here. Come here. Come here. You should make the judgement.

852
00:42:55,770 --> 00:42:57,750
How can the warning line be pulled, horizontally

853
00:42:57,850 --> 00:42:58,840
or aslant?

854
00:43:00,170 --> 00:43:01,210
It should be pulled vertically.

855
00:43:05,700 --> 00:43:06,780
Stand up. Stand up. Stand up.

856
00:43:55,420 --> 00:43:56,350
There's something wrong

857
00:43:57,250 --> 00:43:58,200
with the plaster.

858
00:44:00,800 --> 00:44:01,780
What's it?

859
00:44:03,720 --> 00:44:04,920
I'm just the foreign shit.

860
00:44:05,700 --> 00:44:06,780
I don't know about it.

861
00:44:11,050 --> 00:44:13,030
You're a chemist who does your own business,

862
00:44:13,030 --> 00:44:14,600
but not a loafer who's in charge of some sluggards.

863
00:44:14,600 --> 00:44:15,750
How can't you know about it?

864
00:44:15,920 --> 00:44:17,030
For someone like me,

865
00:44:17,870 --> 00:44:20,030
it's hard to do my own business.

866
00:44:20,150 --> 00:44:22,100
I can at most care for something that happens to my neighbors.

867
00:44:22,250 --> 00:44:23,110
I can give you some help

868
00:44:23,110 --> 00:44:25,190
for your case.

869
00:44:25,450 --> 00:44:28,070
But the death of Diplomatist Gu is closely related to the rise and fall of the nation,

870
00:44:28,070 --> 00:44:29,800
shouldn't everyone take his own responsibility?

871
00:44:30,450 --> 00:44:32,040
Something related to the prosperity of the nation is significant.

872
00:44:32,350 --> 00:44:33,770
You can go to find Secretary General Ding

873
00:44:33,850 --> 00:44:36,140
who cares for the people and wins the popular support.

874
00:44:36,450 --> 00:44:37,230
Leave

875
00:44:38,220 --> 00:44:39,210
me behind.

876
00:44:39,950 --> 00:44:41,960
Brother Junyao.

877
00:44:42,600 --> 00:44:44,270
The case that happened among the people

878
00:44:44,650 --> 00:44:46,890
