879
00:44:47,850 --> 00:44:48,680
I'll follow nothing

880
00:44:48,920 --> 00:44:50,470
but the generally acknowledged truth.

881
00:44:50,820 --> 00:44:52,140
For you,

882
00:44:52,140 --> 00:44:53,550
the diplomatist dying on his wedding is a big case

883
00:44:53,750 --> 00:44:55,660
while my chemical fertilizer plant stopping work and production

884
00:44:56,350 --> 00:44:57,450
is a minor thing.

885
00:44:59,870 --> 00:45:01,230
It's easy to deal with it.

886
00:45:01,450 --> 00:45:02,700
The leader of those rogues, Shi,

887
00:45:02,700 --> 00:45:04,620
has been the card parent of my master for decades.

888
00:45:04,770 --> 00:45:06,190
Tell him to meet me in the market

889
00:45:06,220 --> 00:45:08,430
near the wharf.

890
00:45:12,400 --> 00:45:13,630
Do you remember

891
00:45:14,400 --> 00:45:15,610
what I burnt here last time?

892
00:45:18,520 --> 00:45:19,260
Phosphorus.

