00:45:33,720 --> 00:45:34,670
by a poison, knife or gun.

901
00:45:36,950 --> 00:45:38,590
Why should it be that devious?

902
00:45:39,800 --> 00:45:41,090
Go ask the murderer.

903
00:45:52,820 --> 00:45:55,360
It's the first time I've observed you, Brother Junyao, in such a close distance.

904
00:45:56,320 --> 00:45:59,330
You do have a dignified appearance and you're like a jade tree in the wind at that time.

905
00:45:59,400 --> 00:46:01,890
I can dimly feel your sorrow through your expression,

906
00:46:01,890 --> 00:46:03,230
but you're wise for sure.

907
00:46:05,020 --> 00:46:06,180
Please have a look at this one.

908
00:46:11,470 --> 00:46:12,320
What's it?

909
00:46:12,750 --> 00:46:14,310
The one I got in the trash can of Gu Weiliang that day.

910
00:46:21,520 --> 00:46:23,250
Why haven't you told me earlier?

